{"tid":484870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook：日後需用戶上載真人照片以確認帳號身份","createTime":"2017-11-30T12:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T10:36:09.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":134,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"fbae96665e1c64d75801e79c616fb18c1242ff4c","tid":484870,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"不少手機最近都以面容辨識功能作招徠，想不到就連 Facebook 都開始測試類似技術。最近有用戶發現，Facebook 向他們發出身份核實的通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，要求用戶上載一幅清楚看到相貌的相片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用作核實帳號是真人用戶而不是機械人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1130-2a-768x587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F1130-2a-768x587.jpg&h=07d46614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/11/30/facebook-use-selfie-to-verify-user/life-tech/social-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2Ffacebook-use-selfie-to-verify-user%2Flife-tech%2Fsocial-network%2F&d=vzobyLwFp2vGH3L1F%2B0jiwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=070400a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/11/30/facebook-use-selfie-to-verify-user/life-tech/social-network/</a></div>"},{"pid":"5f1a69c166c9c7b93554eb5ac56ad76951f2fe27","tid":484870,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"據悉 Facebook 自今年年初就開始類似的測試，不過最近更多用戶被要求提供自拍照核實身份。Facebook 回應傳媒查詢時表示，自拍照核實程序能夠幫助他們抓出可疑的活動，包括以假身份註冊帳號、發送大量朋友邀請、製作有問題廣告等。Facebook 表示整個過程都會自動化，當發現帳號有問題就會要求提交自拍照。<br />\n<br />\n用戶需要上載未於 Facebook 發表過的相片，一旦核實過程完成，Facebook 就會將上載的相片從伺服器永久刪除。Facebook 重申，以自拍照核實身份只是他們採用的其中一種方法。"},{"pid":"800f5343be6772add5455d1c93e61dcbe8e504bc","tid":484870,"uid":119330,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:37:38.000Z","msg":"公司ac呢？？？"},{"pid":"427eecdb2c9c6d048c2fb1fc5153847ab33772d6","tid":484870,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:47:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公司ac呢？？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公司最大粒果個lor"},{"pid":"8dbf26ccd4061b0cbf9c732bc7a40a107c5cc7b5","tid":484870,"uid":143241,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:48:21.000Z","msg":"遲早學大陸咁實名制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cac9d160259631db64d1e02791108af9628c07","tid":484870,"uid":26770,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲早學大陸咁實名制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府換新身分證<br />\nfacebook奶共<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姐係你FACEBOOK講咩政府一定知"},{"pid":"5baa20f3a4e8f2cfabf782588b9a4322ccb1c92a","tid":484870,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公司ac呢？？？</blockquote><br />\n公司註冊證<br />\n或者俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e20f390af5eab60a2f155e65862836b7393798","tid":484870,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲早學大陸咁實名制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遲早經高登，集體走佬"},{"pid":"2227188f8625ca6be1f0fcd838925d82e926bce3","tid":484870,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遲早學大陸咁實名制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府換新身分證<br />\nfacebook奶共<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姐係你FACEBOOK講咩政府一定知</blockquote><br />\n出街去到邊都有cam影住啦"},{"pid":"dd50f1c2b2b70cfb1cd278f4d242b93b91553410","tid":484870,"uid":3773,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:55:04.000Z","msg":"而家都少上，大不了 del a